  Your Selfie: <input type="file" name="selfPic" accept="image/*"><br><br> 
  Give us a Title: <input type="text" name="title" placeholder="Check out my look!" id="selfie-title"><br><br> 
  What products did you use? <input type="text" name="products" placeholder="Maybe it's..." id="selfie-products"><br><br> 
  Tell us about it! <br><textarea name="comment" id="comment" cols="30"
  rows="10" maxlength="150" placeholder="This only took 10 minutes!"></textarea><br><br>
  <button type="submit" id="submit">Submit</button>
</form>